# Multi-GPU training MONAI example with PyTorch

## build MONAI container 
using ./build_container.sh

## multi-GPU slurm job submission on single node and multiNode
1. modify the USER definition section in the launch_**.sh
2. Submit a SLURM job script launch.sh to launch a training

## Single-node multi-GPU interactive run
1. use ood to request resources
2. modifiy the USER definition section in interactive.sh   
3. run ./interactive.sh
